To build this project:

1. 'git submodule init'
2. 'git submodule update'
3. Open "Simplified.xcodeproj" and build as normal.


To build this project with Adobe RMSDK support:

1. Copy the RMSDK root folder to $(SRCROOT)/adobe-rmsdk
2. Add the configuration file Simplified+RMSDK.xcconfig to the target Simplified.
3. Add the configuration file RDServices+RMSDK.xcconfig to the target RDServices.
4. Add the configuration file ePub3+RMSDK.xcconfig to the targets ePub3 and ePub3-iOS.
